dataSource.query:
SELECT
	event_name AS Variant,
    "Number of Cases",
	"Asset creation to deactivation (days)",
    "Asset created after capitalization (%)",
    "Asset acquisition with cap. date in the past (%)"
FROM (
	SELECT
    	count(case_id) AS "Number of Cases",
        event_name AS Variant,
        AVG ( "4 - Lead time from start - Asset master deactivated") * 100  
        	AS "Asset creation to deactivation (days)", 
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Asset master created after capitalization") *100
        	AS "Asset created after capitalization (%)",
        AVG ("2 - Blocker - Asset acquisition with capitalization date in the past" ) * 100
        	AS "Asset acquisition with cap. date in the past (%)"
	FROM THIS_PROCESS
	GROUP BY 2
) AS sub
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 5
